眾都吹奏緊既野</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有咩可以做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>正所謂「識睇一定睇comment」<br />\n1）我地要多啲係唔同post下面貼行動文宣同出下發夢注意事項post<br />\n2）仲有要係街airdrop啲文宣俾人</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeba0153328451e2b39ec1adbfde5a7c3311d3aa","tid":1701623,"uid":48315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"係阿 勇武要做野<br />\n最好幾日前通知哂啲狗<br />\n然後比佢SET好哂野<br />\n全部勇武企定定陣地戰<br />\n之後比人拉哂<br />\n啲人唔出黎就係連登屌兩句話佢地廢 激佢地出黎<br />\n咁就係你既做野啦 阿SIR 明架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都ON99 勇武手足要做野自己即興 <br />\n好似琴日咁就係最完美"},{"pid":"686f72e4cfa2b907b7e2b861d20bfc31d6ab0cb0","tid":1701623,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"勇武而家快閃<br />\n唔會通知你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你真係勇武點會唔知同上嚟問<br />\n收皮啦sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312bbb48509bb6509f9f488de7739473e1a9feb1","tid":1701623,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"關你咩事 ?"},{"pid":"496758403028a69ffc719aaf5d6cbb6a3dbecc82","tid":1701623,"uid":253253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"休息中, 明天先啦"},{"pid":"68f3a40cb4216ed9c75ca72c0f7aef88f62d2a10","tid":1701623,"uid":30921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"阿sir今日要拉幾多個"},{"pid":"ef0aead148e18172e0f3b1bbede86022aeafcaf6","tid":1701623,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"